name: Iconduck
description:
With this this Figma Plugin for Iconduck, you can search through 120,000+ free icons, emojis, graphics, flags, illustrations and clipart to find the perfect icon, vector or SVG for your project.


Simply search, click on a result, and the vector (aka SVG) will be added to your design. It scales infinitely large or small.


Iconduck is a platform of 120,000+ free open source icons (of all sorts) that you can use for personal and commercial projects.


All icons are listed as open source, under licenses such as: CCO, MIT License, Creative Commons, Unlicense, Apache and more.


For more information on Iconduck, to download PNG versions of any icons, or to be notified when new icons are added, please visit us at: iconduck.com
